--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-08-24)
B: Remove single quotes from 'haproxy.cfg'
B: Actually fix 'haproxy_stats_uri' variable in template

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-08-24)
B: Change default 'haproxy_stats_uri' to official default (/haproxy?stats)

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-08-24)
F: Add support for 'haproxy_stats_defaults_state' and 'haproxy_stats_listen_state' options
F: Remove support for 'haproxy_stats_state' option
I: Change default 'haproxy_stats_uri' to official default (/haproxy?stats)
I: Remove default stats user 'admin'
I: Minor documentation corrections and improvements

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-08-24)
B: Remove single quotes from 'haproxy_stats_show_node' option (only digits, letters, hyphen or underscode are supported)

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-08-24)
F: Add support for 'stats' options

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-06-01)
F: Initial release
